During the interview, Mr. SHANEMCARDLE focused on the response and challenges of multinational companies under the Russian and Ukraine War and the Global Geopolical Transformation Bureau, the interest pattern and opportunity challenge behind the energy transformation, the global sharing and localization strategy of data in the background of the national security, etc. He gave his thoughts and answers.

