** FT Chinese website **: The Russian -Ukraine conflict is still continuing, which not only has a huge impact on the energy market, but also seriously affects the global supply chain. Can you please share your observation and understanding of this issue?

** SHANE MCARDLE **: This war that is still ongoing has a significant influence on the global business world and the industrial chain industry. I think even it has completely changed the European mentality. Safety is now the first priority of everyone. We have to achieve safety through all aspects. Of course, the safety of energy is also one of the very important parts.

